{"tid":2355332,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"物管股顯著造好　十部委發通知完善物管價格形成機制","createTime":"2021-01-06T05:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T05:09:21.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b1adb547996dfe9176b954dc4153108c40d55e3a","tid":2355332,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:01:38.000Z","msg":"物業管理股顯著造好，保利物業(<a href=\"http://06049.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F06049.HK&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=3039fbf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">06049.HK</a>)急升逾16%，現升近15%，報66元，升8.65元，碧桂園服務(<a href=\"http://06098.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F06098.HK&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=4719fe70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">06098.HK</a>)升13%，報57.4元，升6.65元，雅生活服務(<a href=\"http://03319.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03319.HK&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=c611097d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03319.HK</a>)升13%，報36.15元，新城悅服務(<a href=\"http://01755.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01755.HK&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=2054145f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01755.HK</a>)急升近16%，報19.64元，升2.7元。中海物業(<a href=\"http://02669.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02669.HK&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=405ba285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02669.HK</a>)升12%，報4.42元。 住建部、發改委及銀保監凡十個部委發布「關於加強改進住宅物業管理工作的通知」，內容涵蓋完善物業服務價格形成機制、推動發展生活服務等方面，包括鼓勵有條件的物業服務企業向養老、托幼、家政、健康、房屋經紀、快遞收發等領域延伸，探索「物業服務+生活服務」模式，滿足居民多樣化多層次居住生活需求。 摩根士丹利的報告預期，新政策會加快物管服務市場化，特別是潛在物業管理收費的提升，探索社區增值服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2373626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Ffinance%2F2373626&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=60f6d3aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2373626</a>"},{"pid":"314336fb0a05868a9c8b6aedf3f0edebdb7231ad","tid":2355332,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:09:21.000Z","msg":"非常時期拉日常post 推時事"}]}